details.description:
Get ready to sip, smile, and slurp your way to happiness at Boba Cucue! We're not just serving bubble tea; we're crafting delightful experiences in every cup. Dive into our vibrant world of refreshing flavors and chewy pearls, where every drink is a mini-celebration. Whether you're a long-time boba fan or curious to try something new, come find your perfect pick-me-up and make your day a little brighter with Boba Cucue!
This is the Boba near you...

reviews_data.review_text: First off the place is super cute, plushies everywhere, and a section with crane machines. Second, the boba is super tasty. My friend got the Vietnamese coffee with tapioca boba and I got the lychee green tea with crystal boba. The lychee green tea was so refreshing as it was pretty warm that day. The Vietnamese coffee’s flavors complimented each other so well. Third, the owner was so nice and he has so many ideas for his shop. The owner stoped and talked with us while we sipped on our drinks. He sounds so passionate about his shop and is trying to cater his menu based on what his customers want. If you like boba drinks and cuteness please check it out. Not a lot of sitting room but the cups are super portable so you can shop and sip!
reviews_data.owner_answer:
Aww, thank you for this bobalicious review Emma! 🧋💖
We’re blushing harder than our strawberry milk tea right now. Plushies everywhere? Guilty. Crane machines? Also guilty. Vietnamese coffee and lychee green tea? You clearly know how to order like a boba boss. 😎
It was such a joy chatting with you both—my brain is basically a bubble tea shaker, always mixing up new ideas, so thank you for letting me ramble while you sipped. I’m on a mission to make this place the unofficial HQ of tasty drinks and chaotic cuteness, and your kind words just fueled me like a double shot of espresso boba.
Also, yes, our seating situation is basically “musical chairs but with no music and fewer chairs,” so we made sure our cups are ready for adventure. Shop, sip, conquer the world. 💪
Come back soon—we’ll save a plushie seat for you (or at least a crane machine that almost lets you win). 🐻

reviews_data.review_text: such a cute place!! my mom and i were visiting and stopped by boba cucue. the environment is very calming and friendly. the workers were so sweet! i got the matcha bubble tea and i won a free bunny at the claw machine :D
reviews_data.owner_answer:
You had us at “free bunny” 🐰💚
Thank you so much for hopping by with your mom—we’re thrilled you found our little boba haven as calming and friendly as a bunny doing yoga. Our team works hard to make sure every visit feels like a hug in drink form, and matcha bubble tea is basically our way of saying “we love you” in green.
Also, major claw machine flex! That bunny now holds honorary citizenship at Boba Cucue. We hope it’s living its best life and maybe even helping you pick your next drink. Come back soon—we’ll keep the vibes chill, the drinks tasty, and the claw machine slightly rigged in your favor (just kidding… mostly). 🧋

reviews_data.review_text: Very cute boba shop in-between Under Armor and Old Navy. I got the Honey Milk Bubble which tasted great! The place itself is tiny but they offer additional seating outside.
reviews_data.owner_answer:
Nestled between Under Armour and Old Navy, we like to think of ourselves as the sweet spot where fashion meets flavor. Tiny on the inside, but big on boba energy—and yes, we’ve got outdoor seating so you can sip in style while judging people’s shopping hauls (we won’t tell).
So glad you enjoyed the Honey Milk Bubble—it’s basically liquid sunshine with a chewy plot twist. Come back soon for more drinks, more vibes, and maybe even a plushie sighting or claw machine victory. We’ll be here, tiny but mighty!

reviews_data.review_text:
Katelyn was so beautiful and amazing! I came inside  so not having an idea of what I wanted I asked her what was her favorite thing on the menu she gave me several recommendations until I found the one that I would like. She gave me a couple options of how to do my drink and she made it SOOO PERFECT!! I definitely will be back just for the amazing customer service from Katelyn and the gentleman as well let me try out their claw machine it was an amazing experience!!10000000/ we recommend !!!!!!! Katelyn need a raise ! ❤️❤️❤️❤️

They did have one lady there who was a little off putting just slouching on her phone did not seem interested to even be at work .
reviews_data.owner_answer:
Hi Ylanie, thanks for the review and the feedback. Yes, Katlyn and Richard are our stars.  The other lady you mentioned is Keily, she is one of our fastest and hardest working teammates,  you caught her catching a break after we had a wave of customers. But this teaches us a valuable lession which is "No matter what, we need to be a 100% attentive towards our guests".
We'll make sure our boba is the only thing putting our customers to sleep, not our service!
Thanks from boba cucue
